Too busy to follow up the lead himself, Batman sends Azrael on a mission to Florida to recapture Bane. Bane has redesigned the super steroid Venom, and is looking to sell it to a Santa Priscan general. Azrael and Nomoz investigate, and are captured by Bane. Attempting to use the addictive properties of Venom to enslave Azrael, Bane injects him with the drug. Azrael is able to control his cravings and free himself, leading to the rematch of their epic battle during Knightfall.
